add a third scene (e.g., “Paused”)
⚠️ Common Student Confusions
“Why do we need an Engine class?”

Answer:
👉 Without it, control is scattered and scaling becomes painful

“Why not just switch scenes directly in main?”

Answer:
👉 Because scenes should be self-contained and reusable

“Why do we need onEnter/onExit?”

Answer:
👉 To safely manage:

input listeners
resources
transitions
“Why not just use global variables?”

Answer:
👉 Globals scale poorly and hide dependencies

